properties.Name: Application
properties.Description: A form upon which the prospective insured states or declares facts requested by the insurer on the basis of which the insurer decides whether to accept the risk, modify coverage offered or decline the risk.

Columns.Name: ApplicationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Application.

Columns.Name: ApplicationDate
Columns.Description: The date that the Application was made.

Columns.Name: BackdatedDate
Columns.Description:
A procedure in which the effective date of a policy is earlier than the application date.   Backdating is often used to make the age at issue lower than it actually was in order to get a lower premium.   

Some state laws limit the time to which the policies can be backdated.

Columns.Name: ProposedInsuredName
Columns.Description: The name of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: AkaName
Columns.Description: The AKA name of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: MaidenName
Columns.Description: The maiden name of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: PolicyholderName
Columns.Description: The name of the Policyholder, if different from the Proposed Insured.

Columns.Name: AgentName
Columns.Description: The name of the Agent.

Columns.Name: DisclosureProvidedApplicantDate
Columns.Description: When required by state law, the agent must provide and sign a form attesting that a disclosure statement has been given to the applicant.

Columns.Name: DisclosureStatement
Columns.Description:
A form that authorizes the disclosure of personal information that is obtained in connection with insurance transactions.    Insurers are required by law to give applicants advance notice of such information practices.   The form must state the nature and kind of information collected and to whom information may be disclosed.

When required by state law, the agent must provide and sign a form attesting that a disclosure statement has been given to the applicant.

Columns.Name: Gender
Columns.Description: The gender of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: DateOfBirth
Columns.Description: The date of birth of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: AgeNearestBirthday
Columns.Description: The age as of the nearest birthday of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: PlaceOfBirth
Columns.Description: The place of birth of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: DayTelephoneNumber
Columns.Description: The daytime telephone number of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: NightTelephoneNumber
Columns.Description: The night telephone number of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: PremiumNoticesAddress
Columns.Description: The address to which premium notices are to be sent of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ResidenceAddress
Columns.Description: The residence address of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: SocialSecurityNumber
Columns.Description: The social security number of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: AmountOfExistingSmliInsurance
Columns.Description: The current amount of SMLI insurance in effect of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: SmokedCigarettesWithinLast12MonthsIndicator
Columns.Description: A flag or indicator indicating that the proposed insured has regularly smoked cigarettes within the last 12 months.

Columns.Name: SmokedCigarsWithinLast12MonthsIndicator
Columns.Description: A flag or indicator indicating that the proposed insured has regularly smoked cigars within the last 12 months.

Columns.Name: SmokedPipeWithinLast12MonthsIndicator
Columns.Description: A flag or indicator indicating that the proposed insured has regularly smoked pipes within the last 12 months.

Columns.Name: BasicPolicyAmountAppliedFor
Columns.Description: The amount of insurance that the proposed insured has applied for.

Columns.Name: InsuranceProductNameAppliedFor
Columns.Description: The name of the Insurance Product that the proposed insured has applied for.

Columns.Name: WaiverOfPremiumIndicator
Columns.Description: A provision of a Life Insurance Policy which continues coverage if the insured becomes totally disabled without further premium payments.

Columns.Name: DividendPaymentMethod
Columns.Description: The method of dividend payments specified for the policy.

Columns.Name: PremiumPaymentFrequencyDesired
Columns.Description: The desired frequency of payment requested by the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: NamedBeneficiaries
Columns.Description: The beneficiaries named by the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: BeneficiariesRelationship
Columns.Description: The relationship of the beneficiaries to the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: CoverageReplacesExistingLifeInsuranceCoverageIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the proposed coverage replaces existing life insurance coverage in effect at the present time.

Columns.Name: CoverageAugmentsExistingLifeInsuranceCoverageIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the proposed coverage augments existing life insurance coverage in effect at the present time.

Columns.Name: GroupCoverageName
Columns.Description: The name of the Group providing group coverage to the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: SpecialRequests
Columns.Description: Special requests made by the proposed insured as part of the application for insurance.

Columns.Name: EmployerName
Columns.Description: The name of the Employer of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: EmployerAddress
Columns.Description: The address of the Employer of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: JobTitle
Columns.Description: The Job Title of the proposed insured at the associated Employment.

Columns.Name: DescriptionOfDuties
Columns.Description: A description of employment duties of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: YearsEmployed
Columns.Description: The number of years of employment at the associated Employer by the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: FirstEmploymentDate
Columns.Description: The first date of employment at the associated employment by the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: IntendsToResideOutsideOfUsOrCanadaIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator indicating that the proposed insured intends to reside outside of the US or Canada.

Columns.Name: PreviousLifeInsuranceApplicationsRejectedIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator that previous life insurance application made by the proposed insured were rejected.

Columns.Name: ParticipatesInParachutingIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator that the proposed insured participates in parachuting activities.

Columns.Name: ParticipatesInMotorRacingIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator that the proposed insured participates in motor racing activities.

Columns.Name: ParticipatesInHazardousHobbyIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator that the proposed insured participates in a hazardous hobby or similar activities.

Columns.Name: NumberCommercialFlightsInLast12Months
Columns.Description: The number of commercial flights taken by the proposed insured in the last 12 months.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfBrainIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the brain.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfNervousSystemIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the nervous system.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfHeartIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the heart.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfBloodVesselsIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the blood vessels.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfLungsIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the lungs.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfStomachOrIntestinesIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the stomach or intestines.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfSkinIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the skin.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfGlandsIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the glands.

Columns.Name: SufferedFromIllnessDiseaseOfEyesVisionIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured suffered from an illness or disease of the eyes or related to vision.

Columns.Name: TreatedForChestPainIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for chest pain.

Columns.Name: TreatedForDizzinessIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for dizziness.

Columns.Name: TreatedForFaintingIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for fainting.

Columns.Name: TreatedForConvulsionsIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for convulsions.

Columns.Name: TreatedForAllergiesAsthmaIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for allergies or asthma.

Columns.Name: TreatedForParalysisStrokeIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for paralysis or stroke.

Columns.Name: TreatedForAlcoholismIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for alcoholism.

Columns.Name: TreatedForMentalNervousDisorderIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for mental or nervous disorders.

Columns.Name: TreatedForDeformityCongenitalDisorderIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for deformities or congenital disorders.

Columns.Name: TakingTakenMedicineForConditionDiseaseIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured is or has taken medication for a condition or disease.

Columns.Name: DisorderOfMenstruationPregnancyFemaleOrgansIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured has been treated for menstruation, pregnancy or female organ disorders or conditions.

Columns.Name: CurrentlyPregnantIndicator
Columns.Description: An indicator denoting that the proposed insured is currently pregnant.

Columns.Name: NumberOfChildren
Columns.Description: The number of children of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: Height
Columns.Description: The height of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: Weight
Columns.Description: The weight of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: AmountWeightChangedInLastTwoYears
Columns.Description: The amount of weight change in the last two years of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: FatherDateOfBirth
Columns.Description: The date of birth of the proposed insured's father.

Columns.Name: MotherDateOfBirth
Columns.Description: The date of birth of the proposed insured's mother.

Columns.Name: FatherCurrentAge
Columns.Description: The current age of the proposed insured's father.

Columns.Name: MotherCurrentAge
Columns.Description: The current age of the proposed insured's mother.

Columns.Name: FatherCurrentHealthCondition
Columns.Description: The current health condition of the proposed insured's father.

Columns.Name: MotherCurrentHealthCondition
Columns.Description: The current health condition of the proposed insured's mother.

Columns.Name: NumberOfBrothers
Columns.Description: The number of brothers of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: NumberOfSisters
Columns.Description: The number of sisters of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: SystolicBloodPressure
Columns.Description: The systolic blood pressure of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: DiastolicBloodPressure
Columns.Description: The diastolic blood pressure of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ChestInspiration
Columns.Description: The chest inspiration of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ChestExpiration
Columns.Description: The chest expiration of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: Waist
Columns.Description: The waist measurement of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: PulseRate
Columns.Description: The resting pulse rate of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: PulseQuality
Columns.Description: The quality of the resting pulse judged by the examiner.

Columns.Name: IrregularitiesPerMinute
Columns.Description: The number of pulse irregularities per minute of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: AlbuminTestResults
Columns.Description: The albumin test results of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: SugarTestResults
Columns.Description: The sugar test results of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ExaminerNotes
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information provided by the examiner of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ExaminerTitle
Columns.Description: The medical title of the examiner (nurse, MD etc.)

Columns.Name: ExaminerName
Columns.Description: The name of the examiner.

Columns.Name: ExaminationDate
Columns.Description: The date of the application examination of the proposed insured.

Columns.Name: ApprovedDate
Columns.Description: The date upon which the person or object to be insured meets the underwriting standards of the insurer.

Columns.Name: DeclinationDate
Columns.Description: The date that the insured was rejected for insurance coverage by the insurer.

Columns.Name: PreparedDate
Columns.Description: The as-of or effective date that the associated information is determined or reported.

Columns.Name: DividendOptionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dividend Option.

Columns.Name: ApplicationReceiptTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Application Receipt Type.

Columns.Name: LifeInsurabilityRiskCategoryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Risk Category.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: PolicyholderId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Policyholder.
